# Ara Sales mobile (Flutter) configuration.
#
# Flutter has no runtime .env; configuration is passed at build/run time via
# --dart-define. This file documents the variables. Example:
#
#   flutter run \
#     --dart-define=API_BASE_URL=http://10.0.2.2:4000 \
#     --dart-define=PING_INTERVAL_SECONDS=300
#
# API_BASE_URL
#   Backend base URL.
#   - Android emulator -> http://10.0.2.2:4000  (host loopback)
#   - iOS simulator    -> http://localhost:4000
#   - Physical device  -> http://<your-LAN-IP>:4000
#
# PING_INTERVAL_SECONDS
#   GPS ping cadence while a work session is active. Spec default: 300 (5 min).
